  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Start of Your Main Phase] By returning this Tamer to the
    bottom of the deck, you may play 1 [Violet Inboots] from your hand without paying
    the cost. Then, if you don't have a Digimon, you may play 1 [Ghostmon] from your
    trash without paying the cost.\n[Your Turn] When any of your Digimon digivolve
    into a Digimon with the [Ghost]\_trait, by suspending this Tamer, that Digimon
    gains \uFF1CRush\uFF1E for the turn. "
